%5B%7B%22title%22%3A%22Won't%20Accept%20Education%20Policy%20Even%20If%20Centre%20Offers%2010%2C000%20Crores%3A%20MK%20Stalin%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EMK%20Stalin%20is%20firm%20in%20his%20stance%20on%20not%20implementing%20the%20National%20Education%20Policy%20(NEP)%20in%20Tamil%20Nadu%20even%20if%20the%20Centre%20offered%20to%20provide%20Rs%2010%2C000%20crore%20in%20funds%20to%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Tamil%20Nadu%20Chief%20Minister%20has%20said%20the%20opposition%20to%20the%20policy%20is%20not%20merely%20over%20%26quot%3Bimposition%20of%20Hindi%26quot%3B%20but%20there%20are%20several%20other%20factors%20that%20would%20have%20serious%20consequences%20on%20the%20future%20of%20students%20and%20the%20social%20justice%20system.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAddressing%20a%20Parent-Teachers%20Association%20event%20in%20Tamil%20Nadu's%20Cuddalore%2C%20Mr%20Stalin%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BWe%20are%20not%20opposed%20to%20any%20language%20but%20will%20remain%20firm%20in%20opposing%20its%20imposition.%20We%20are%20not%20opposing%20the%20NEP%20only%20for%20the%20attempt%20to%20thrust%20Hindi%20but%20for%20several%20other%20reasons%20as%20well.%20The%20NEP%20is%20regressive.%20It%20will%20drive%20students%20away%20from%20schools.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERead%20more%3A%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Ftamil-nadu-linguistic-minorities-forum-urges-mk-stalin-to-implement-nep-amid-row-over-hindi-7749883%5C%22%3ETamil%20Nadu%20Linguistic%20Minorities%20Forum%20Urges%20MK%20Stalin%20To%20Implement%20NEP%20Amid%20Row%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EApart%20from%20'denying'%20financial%20aid%20to%20SC%2FST%20and%20BC%20students%2C%20which%20is%20now%20being%20provided%2C%20the%20NEP%20proposed%20public%20exams%20for%20third%2C%20fifth%2C%20and%20eighth%20standards%2C%20besides%20introducing%20a%20common%20entrance%20test%20for%20admissions%20to%20arts%20and%20science%20colleges%2C%20the%20Chief%20Minister%20claimed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20row%20over%20the%20implementation%20of%20the%20policy%20in%20Tamil%20Nadu%20and%20the%20three-language%20formula%20in%20NEP%20has%20escalated%20and%20Mr%20Stalin%20had%20written%20to%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%2C%20complaining%20that%20Education%20Minister%20Dharmendra%20Pradhan%20had%20threatened%20to%20withhold%20Rs%202%2C000%20crore%20for%20a%20centrally%20sponsored%20initiative%2C%20the%20Samagra%20Shiksha%20Abhiyan%2C%20unless%20Tamil%20Nadu%20implemented%20the%20NEP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESamagra%20Shiksha%20Abhiyan%20seeks%20to%20integrate%20vocational%20education%20with%20general%20academic%20education%20by%20linking%20it%20to%20the%20NEP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Centre%20says%20Tamil%20Nadu%20will%20get%20Rs%202%2C000%20crore%20if%20the%20state%20implements%20the%20NEP.%20I%20wish%20to%20say%20that%20we%20will%20not%20agree%20to%20the%20NEP%20even%20if%20the%20Centre%20offers%20Rs%2010%2C000%20crore.%20I%20will%20not%20allow%20the%20NEP%20and%20commit%20the%20sin%20of%20pushing%20Tamil%20Nadu%20backwards%20by%202%2C000%20years%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Stalin%20said%20today.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Stalin%20earlier%20said%20%26quot%3BThe%20policy%20was%20brought%20to%20nurture%20Hindi%20and%20not%20education.%20It's%20camouflaged%20in%20the%20name%20of%20education%20policy%20as%20it%20would%20be%20opposed%20if%20done%20directly%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20Education%20Minister%20Said%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fdharmendra-pradhan-national-education-policy-tamil-nadu-bjp-dmk-ndtv-exclusive-creating-anti-delhi-narrative-education-minister-hits-back-at-mk-stalin-7763064%5C%22%3ESpeaking%20to%20NDTV%2C%20Mr%20Pradhan%20responded%20sharply%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20Mr%20Stalin's%20claims%20and%20criticism%20over%20the%20policy%20and%20said%20the%20Tamil%20Nadu%20Chief%20Minister%20is%20creating%20a%20%26quot%3Bfalse%20narrative%26quot%3B%20of%20Hindi%20imposition%2C%20which%20is%20politically%20motivated.%20The%20minister%20insisted%20that%20Tamil%20Nadu%20had%20agreed%20to%20the%20implementation%20of%20the%20National%20Education%20Policy%20earlier%2C%20but%20made%20a%20U-turn%20on%20the%20issue%20for%20political%20reasons.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnder%20the%20three-language%20formula%20which%20is%20part%20of%20the%20National%20Education%20Policy%20(NEP)%2C%202020%2C%20every%20school%20student%20has%20to%20study%20at%20least%20three%20languages.%20The%20Centre%20has%20said%20this%20clause%20is%20necessary%20as%20previous%20education%20policies%20neglected%20the%20systematic%20teaching%20of%20Indian%20languages%20leading%20to%20an%20%26quot%3Bover-reliance%26quot%3B%20on%20foreign%20languages%20and%20it%20aims%20to%20restore%20languages%20like%20Tamil%20to%20their%20%26quot%3Brightful%20place%20in%20education%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20back-and-forth%20between%20the%20Centre%20and%20Tamil%20Nadu%20government%20continued%20and%20Mr%20Pradhan%20wrote%20a%20letter%20to%20Mr%20Stalin%20explaining%20the%20policy.%20He%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20three-language%20formula%20is%20a%20pattern%20of%20the%20country.%20Almost%20all%20states%20have%20been%20implementing%20it%20since%20the%20mid-1960s.%20I%20know%20the%20position%20of%20Tamil%20Nadu.%20I%20know%20there%20are%20some%20issues%2C%20they%20adopted%20a%20two-language%20formula.%20The%20NEP%2C%20envisioned%20by%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi's%20government%2C%20has%20emphasized%20the%20three-language%20formula.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20you%20talk%20about%20the%20three-language%20formula%2C%20unnecessarily%20a%20political%20line%20has%20been%20taken%20and%20they%20are%20talking%20about%20the%20imposition%20of%20Hindi%20in%20Tamil%20Nadu.%20Nowhere%20in%20the%20NEP%20have%20we%20suggested%20that%20there%20will%20be%20an%20imposition%20of%20any%20particular%20language%20in%20any%20particular%20state.%20I%20have%20also%20written%20to%20the%20honourable%20chief%20minister%20of%20Tamil%20Nadu%20about%20this%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20explained.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Pradhan%20said%20it%20was%20okay%20that%20Tamil%20Nadu%20chose%20to%20teach%20in%20Tamil%20and%20English%2C%20but%20asked%20what%20would%20happen%20to%20students%20living%20in%20the%20border%20areas%20of%20the%20state%20who%20wanted%20to%20learn%20Kannada%2C%20Telugu%2C%20Malayalam%2C%20Marathi%20or%20Odia%20for%20employment%20purposes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EFund%20Cut%20Claims%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Mr%20Stalin's%20claims%20that%20over%20Rs%202%2C000%20crore%20had%20been%20withheld%20from%20Tamil%20Nadu%20for%20the%20Samagra%20Shiksha%20Abhiyan%20-%20which%20seeks%20to%20integrate%20vocational%20education%20with%20general%20academic%20education%20-%20by%20linking%20it%20to%20the%20NEP%2C%20which%20the%20chief%20minister%20called%20%26quot%3Bblackmail%20and%20coercion%26quot%3B%2C%20Mr%20Pradhan%20said%20the%20use%20of%20such%20%26quot%3Bderogatory%20words%20is%20condemnable%20in%20a%20democracy%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe%20is%20speaking%20a%20politically%20motivated%20language...%20They%20have%20created%20a%20fear%20psychosis%20that%20the%20Union%20government%20is%20going%20to%20impose%20Hindi.%20Who%20is%20going%20to%20impose%20Hindi%3F%20I%20am%20an%20Odia-speaking%20person.%20Even%20in%20my%20state%2C%20a%20three-language%20formula%20has%20been%20implemented.%20The%20same%20is%20true%20for%20Punjab%20and%20West%20Bengal.%20Nowhere%20is%20Hindi%20being%20imposed%20as%20a%20third%20language.%20So%2C%20you%20(Mr%20Stalin%20and%20the%20DMK)%20have%20a%20political%20motivation%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20minister%20pointed%20out%20that%20the%20PM-Poshan%20(mid-day%20meal)%20scheme%20had%20not%20been%20stopped%20in%20Tamil%20Nadu%20and%20alleged%20that%20the%20state%20government%2C%20due%20to%20its%20%26quot%3Brigid%20stand%26quot%3B%2C%20was%20depriving%20students%20of%20another%20Rs%202%2C000%20crore%20under%20the%20PM%20SHRI%20scheme.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(With%20inputs%20from%20PTI)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1740232080000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2022-07%2F4kjeo7so_mk-stalin_625x300_05_July_22.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fnep-2020-wont-accept-national-education-policy-even-if-offered-rs-10-000-crore-mk-stalin-tamil-nadu-7770396%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22MK%20Stalin%20is%20firm%20in%20his%20stance%20on%20not%20implementing%20the%20National%20Education%20Policy%20(NEP)%20in%20Tamil%20Nadu%20even%20if%20the%20Centre%20offered%20to%20provide%20Rs%2010%2C000%20crore%20in%20funds%20to%20the%20state.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fnep-2020-wont-accept-national-education-policy-even-if-offered-rs-10-000-crore-mk-stalin-tamil-nadu-7770396%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22I%20moved%20from%20Chicago%20to%20San%20Diego%20for%20love.%20My%20friends%20were%20jealous%2C%20but%20I%20couldn't%20leave%20the%20California%20city%20fast%20enough.%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%228256%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22View%20of%20land%20jutting%20out%20into%20sea%20at%20La%20Jolla%20Cove%20%2C%20San%20Diego%2C%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67b7398b7bb3f854015d5707%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%225504%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20view%20of%20La%20Jolla%20Cove%20in%20San%20Diego.%3Cp%3ENeil%20Spence%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EI%20moved%20from%20Chicago%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Feverything-you-need-to-know-about-traveling-to-san-diego-california%5C%22%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22false%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESan%20Diego%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20be%20with%20my%20long-distance%20boyfriend%2C%20who's%20now%20my%20husband.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EAlthough%20my%20friends%20were%20jealous%20I%20was%20moving%20to%20a%20sunny%20%26quot%3Bparadise%2C%26quot%3B%20San%20Diego%20wasn't%20for%20me.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EI%20found%20the%20weather%20to%20be%20boring%2C%20and%20I%20didn't%20like%20how%20hard%20it%20was%20to%20get%20around%20without%20a%20car.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmoving-philadelphia-to-chicago-surprising-things-cons-2024-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eliving%20in%20Chicago%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20six%20years%2C%20I%20had%20a%20fulfilling%20career%2C%20great%20friends%2C%20and%20was%20involved%20in%20several%20organizations.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20would've%20happily%20stayed%20there%20forever%2C%20but%20my%20then-boyfriend%20(now%20husband)%20was%20in%20the%20Navy.%20We'd%20been%20in%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flong-distance-fiance-relationship-2023-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elong-distance%20relationship%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20seven%20years%2C%20and%20we%20wanted%20to%20be%20together.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20July%202023%2C%20I%20moved%20to%20where%20he%20was%20currently%20located%3A%20San%20Diego.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20told%20my%20Midwest%20friends%20and%20colleagues%20about%20my%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmoved-to-charming-town-northern-california-hated-it-grass-valley-2024-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emove%20to%20California%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20some%20of%20their%20eyes%20would%20grow%20wide%20with%20envy.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMany%20of%20them%20%E2%80%94%20some%20who'd%20never%20been%20to%20San%20Diego%20%E2%80%94%20would%20tell%20me%20how%20lucky%20I%20was%20to%20move%20to%20a%20sunny%20%26quot%3Bparadise%26quot%3B%20with%20so%20many%20beaches.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20would%20smile%20and%20nod%2C%20but%20I%20was%20actually%20very%20reluctant%20to%20move.%20Eventually%2C%20I%20learned%20firsthand%20why%20the%20sunny%20city%20wasn't%20the%20right%20home%20for%20me.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%221820aba2-5f45-43a2-bd3f-6292cf7f814a%5C%22%3ESan%20Diego's%20sunny%20weather%20bored%20me%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221280%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Author%20Chelsey%20Stone%20smiling%20on%20trail%20in%20San%20Diego%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6793e1e9ae09223df2bb6b49%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22960%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20nice%20weather%20made%20it%20easy%20for%20me%20to%20enjoy%20San%20Diego's%20beautiful%20hiking%20spots%2C%20but%20I%20got%20bored%20of%20all%20the%20sunshine.%3Cp%3EChelsey%20Stone%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAlthough%20many%20of%20my%20Midwest%20friends%20envied%20the%20idea%20of%20year-round%20beach%20weather%20%E2%80%94%20especially%20during%20frigid%20winters%20%E2%80%94%20I%20wasn't%20a%20fan%20of%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHaving%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flos-angeles-things-to-know-before-visiting-from-a-local-2022-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Egrown%20up%20in%20California%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20I%20actually%20took%20perverse%20delight%20in%20the%20adversity%20of%20Chicago's%20cold%20and%20snowy%20winters.%20I%20was%20amazed%20at%20how%20the%20city%20carried%20on%2C%20no%20matter%20the%20weather%20conditions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20loved%20having%20white%20Christmases%20like%20in%20the%20movies%20I%20watched%20as%20a%20kid.%20I%20reveled%20in%20Chicago's%20changing%20seasons%2C%20dining%20outdoors%20in%20the%20spring%20and%20summer%2C%20bundling%20up%20in%20the%20winter%2C%20and%20watching%20the%20leaves%20change%20in%20the%20fall.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20San%20Diego's%20weather%20is%20almost%20always%20sunny%20and%20in%20the%2060s.%20Eventually%2C%20I%20even%20removed%20the%20weather%20app%20from%20my%20phone's%20home%20screen%20because%20I%20felt%20there%20was%20no%20point%20in%20checking%20it%20anymore.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlthough%20the%20sunshine%20was%20nice%20when%20I%20wanted%20to%20visit%20the%20beach%20or%20one%20of%20the%20area's%20great%20hiking%20trails%2C%20I%20grew%20bored%20by%20the%20lack%20of%20seasonal%20change%20and%20even%20missed%20the%20difficulties%20Midwestern%20winters%20can%20bring.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20missed%20needing%20to%20wear%20the%20sweaters%20my%20nana%20had%20knit%20to%20keep%20me%20warm%20in%20Chicago%20%E2%80%94%20and%20being%20able%20to%20comfortably%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchristmas-australia-vs-london-comparison-2020-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Evisit%20the%20beach%20on%20Christmas%3C%2Fa%3E%20just%20felt%20wrong%20to%20me.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22cac0e883-ba59-4197-9efa-d78b06d0f088%5C%22%3EI%20struggled%20to%20adjust%20to%20living%20in%20a%20car-centric%20city%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EBefore%20moving%2C%20I'd%20visited%20my%20partner%20many%20times%2C%20so%20I%20knew%20just%20how%20car-centric%20San%20Diego%20is.%20However%2C%20I%20didn't%20have%20(or%20need)%20a%20car%20in%20Chicago%20and%20had%20no%20desire%20to%20purchase%20or%20own%20one.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESince%20San%20Diego%20is%20also%20a%20sunny%20beach%20town%2C%20I%20assumed%20cycling%20to%20get%20around%20would%20be%20popular%2C%20convenient%2C%20and%20easy%20enough.%20I%20soon%20discovered%20that%20was%20not%20the%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUnfortunately%2C%20many%20of%20the%20city's%20neighborhoods%20and%20downtown%20areas%20didn't%20feel%20well%20connected%20for%20biking.%20I%20struggled%20to%20find%20bike%20lanes%2C%20and%20my%20map%20apps%20often%20directed%20me%20to%20cycle%20on%20roads%20that%20were%20basically%20highways.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEventually%2C%20I%20began%20trying%20to%20run%20or%20walk%20to%20places%20instead%2C%20but%20that%2C%20too%2C%20proved%20challenging%20as%20I%20often%20encountered%20missing%20sidewalks%20or%20busy%20roads.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20bright%20side%2C%20I%20was%20pleasantly%20surprised%20by%20San%20Diego's%20public%20transportation.%20To%20be%20fair%2C%20coming%20from%20Chicago%20%E2%80%94%20a%20big%20city%20with%20extensive%20bus%20and%20train%20options%20%E2%80%94%20I%20had%20very%20low%20expectations.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlthough%20it%20was%20nice%20to%20be%20able%20to%20take%20public%20transit%2C%20it%20sometimes%20took%20me%20an%20hour%20or%20more%20and%20several%20connections%20to%20travel%20throughout%20San%20Diego.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEventually%2C%20I%20accepted%20that%20San%20Diego%20and%20I%20just%20don't%20have%20compatible%20priorities%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20getting%20around.%20Living%20here%20reminded%20me%20how%20much%20I%20prefer%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbest-walkable-cities-for-pedestrians-2019-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewalkable%20cities%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20car-centric%20ones.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22ff374f0d-060e-496b-90d9-05a08d4af668%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3ESometimes%20it%20was%20even%20hard%20to%20enjoy%20the%20beaches%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224320%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22La%20Jolla%20Shores%20beach%20and%20Scripps%20Pier%20in%20San%20Diego%2C%20California%2C%20and%20the%20Pacific%20Ocean.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6793e2c32fcded5e9074a54c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222536%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ESan%20Diego%20is%20beautiful%2C%20but%20it%20was%20hard%20to%20watch%20people%20litter%20and%20leave%20trash%20on%20its%20beaches.%3Cp%3EL.%20Toshio%20Kishiyama%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EMany%20of%20my%20Midwestern%20friends%20were%20jealous%20of%20just%20how%20many%20beautiful%20local%20beaches%20I'd%20have%20access%20to%20in%20San%20Diego.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUnfortunately%2C%20these%20beaches%20also%20drew%20in%20many%20tourists%20and%20visitors%20%E2%80%94%20and%20I%20didn't%20always%20know%20if%20I'd%20be%20able%20to%20fully%20enjoy%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C