earned%20this%2C%20that%20timeline%20had%20to%20change.%20It%20ended%20up%20taking%20about%20seven.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EWe%20unknowingly%20chose%20the%20perfect%20time%20of%20year%20for%20an%20installation.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221179%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22screenshot%20of%20a%20list%20of%20calendar%20events%20on%20a%20phone%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67b5fb177bb3f854015d3b88%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22884%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EWe%20packed%20everything%20up%20in%20August%20and%20did%20the%20carpets%20in%20September.%3Cp%3ETrisha%20Daab%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EOur%20professional%20installation%20was%20scheduled%20for%20early%20September.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fshopping-jewel-osco-every-week-budget-midwest-favorite-things-2025-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elive%20in%20the%20Midwest%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20so%20luckily%2C%20that%20meant%20it%20was%20warm%20enough%20to%20use%20the%20garage%20as%20a%20storage%20space.%20On%20install%20day%2C%20everyone%20was%20also%20able%20to%20be%20outdoors%20to%20get%20out%20of%20the%20way.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENone%20of%20that%20would've%20been%20a%20comfortable%20option%20during%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchicago-remote-worker-meet-people-socialize-freezing-winters-friends-weather-2024-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efrigid%20Chicago%20winter%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Without%20knowing%20it%2C%20we%20picked%20the%20perfect%20time%20for%20the%20renovation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThe%20installers%20may%20not%20be%20willing%20to%20move%20all%20your%20furniture.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22941%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22primary%20bedroom%20after%20replacing%20carpets%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67b5fbc8eb4be2fff9a4fdcf%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22706%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EWe%20have%20a%20lot%20of%20furniture%20in%20our%20primary%20bedroom.%3Cp%3ETrisha%20Daab%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20worth%20looking%20up%20the%20specifics%20of%20your%20carpet-installation%20agreement%20before%20booking%20a%20service%2C%20especially%20if%20you%20have%20some%20large%20furniture%20pieces.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20larger%20rooms%2C%20our%20installers%20were%20able%20to%20move%20most%20of%20the%20furniture%20while%20they%20worked.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20they%20weren't%20allowed%20to%20move%20our%20beds%20because%20of%20some%20specific%20contract%20rule.%20We%20ended%20up%20having%20to%20figure%20out%20how%20to%20move%20and%20store%20those%20ourselves%20before%20the%20installers%20arrived.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EOne%20of%20the%20best%20things%20I%20did%20was%20create%20a%20note%20detailing%20where%20I'd%20packed%20our%20stuff.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221179%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22screenshot%20of%20a%20note%20on%20the%20notes%20app%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67b5f9526630eb10385cf96f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22884%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EOver%20the%20course%20of%20the%20seven-week%20renovation%20process%2C%20I%20made%20a%20lot%20of%20lists.%3Cp%3ETrisha%20Daab%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EBy%20the%20time%20everything%20was%20packed%20up%2C%20stuff%20was%20everywhere%20(including%20in%20my%20car).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fliving-room-trends-styles-in-and-out-interior-designers-2025-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eliving%20room%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20primary%20bath%20were%20full%20of%20primary%20bedroom%20furniture%20and%20boxes.%20The%20kids'%20bathroom%20had%20beds%20and%20bookshelves.%20The%20garage%20and%20basement%20were%20full%20of%20boxes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20throughout%20the%20renovation%2C%20I%20kept%20a%20note%20on%20my%20phone%20called%2C%20%26quot%3BWhere's%20my%20stuff%3F%26quot%3B%20that%20had%20sections%20for%20each%20room%20that%20detailed%20where%20the%20furniture%20and%20boxes%20from%20it%20were%20in%20the%20house.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20note%20became%20invaluable%20when%20we%20moved%20everything%20back%20in%2C%20ensuring%20we%20knew%20where%20it%20all%20went%20before%20unpacking.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20one%20of%20the%20best%20things%20I%20did%20throughout%20the%20renovation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EPutting%20all%20of%20our%20stuff%20back%20felt%20like%20the%20most%20difficult%20part%20of%20getting%20new%20carpets.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22bedroom%20after%20carpet%20instillation%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67b5fd347bb3f854015d3bfe%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EIt%20was%20harder%20to%20put%20everything%20back%20than%20I%20could've%20imagined.%3Cp%3ETrisha%20Daab%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAlthough%20my%20note%20came%20in%20handy%20for%20locating%20items%2C%20putting%20everything%20back%20in%20its%20place%20felt%20like%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fred-flags-look-for-moving-new-home-cleaner-2023-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emoving%20into%20a%20new%20house%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEven%20though%20all%20the%20stuff%20came%20out%20of%20our%20space%2C%20it%20was%20a%20bit%20of%20a%20headache%20trying%20to%20figure%20out%20how%20to%20make%20everything%20fit%20again.%20It%20reminded%20me%20of%20when%20TSA%20searches%20your%20zipped-up%20suitcase%2C%20but%20afterward%2C%20it%20won't%20close.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDespite%20a%20lot%20of%20purging%20during%20packing%2C%20there%20somehow%20didn't%20feel%20like%20we%20had%20enough%20space%20for%20our%20stuff.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EI%20wished%20we'd%20more%20closely%20read%20the%20fine%20print%20of%20our%20carpet%20warranty.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22dog%20sit