20%26quot%3Bgain-of-function%20studies%26quot%3B%20on%20coronavirus%20amid%20allegations%20that%20USAID%20has%20funded%20the%20study%20of%20the%20infectious%20disease.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BChina%20has%20also%20made%20it%20clear%20more%20than%20once%20that%20the%20Wuhan%20Institute%20of%20Virology%20has%20never%20engaged%20in%20gain-of-function%20studies%20of%20coronavirus%2C%26quot%3B%20Chinese%20Foreign%20Ministry%20spokesperson%20Guo%20Jiakun%20told%20a%20media%20briefing%20here%20responding%20to%20allegations%20in%20US%20that%20the%20USAID%20taxpayers'%20money%20was%20used%20to%20fund%20gain-of-function%20studies%20at%20the%20Chinese%20bio-lab.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGain-of-function%20research%20is%20medical%20research%20that%20genetically%20alters%20an%20organism%20in%20a%20way%20that%20may%20enhance%20the%20biological%20functions%20of%20gene%20products.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNever%20has%20it%20designed%2C%20made%20or%20leaked%20COVID-19.%20On%20the%20origins-tracing%20of%20the%20virus%2C%20China%20firmly%20opposes%20all%20forms%20of%20political%20manipulation%26quot%3B%2C%20Guo%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20recent%20American%20media%20reports%2C%20the%20US%20Agency%20for%20International%20Development%20(USAID)%20used%20taxpayers'%20money%20to%20fund%20gain-of-function%20studies%20at%20China's%20Wuhan%20Institute%20of%20Virology%2C%20which%20may%20have%20caused%20the%20COVID-19%20pandemic%2C%20leading%20to%20the%20deaths%20of%20millions%20around%20the%20world.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETrump%20has%20shut%20down%20the%20USAID%20work%20that%20was%20not%20aligned%20with%20American%20strategic%20interests%20and%20wastes%20money.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Wuhan%20bio-lab%20was%20constantly%20under%20scanner%2C%20especially%20during%20the%20previous%20Trump%20presidency.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGuo%20said%20at%20a%20media%20briefing%20on%20February%2012%20here%20that%20%26quot%3BIt%20is%20'extremely%20unlikely'%20that%20the%20COVID-19%20pandemic%20