tps%3A%2F%2Fwww.digital-i.com%2Fnews-articles%2Fpress-release-digital-i-youtube-measurement%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EDigital%20i%20found%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20videos%20lasting%2030%20minutes%20or%20more%20accounted%20for%2073%25%20of%20total%20viewing%20on%20the%20platform%20in%20the%20US%20in%20October%202024%2C%20up%208%25%20from%20a%20year%20earlier.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221424%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Chart%20showing%20increase%20of%20long-form%20viewing%20on%20YouTube%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67b880f27bb3f854015d7511%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22788%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ELong-form%20viewing%20on%20YouTube%20is%20on%20the%20rise.%3Cp%3EDigital%20i%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EYouTube%20isn't%20the%20only%20game%20in%20town%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20free%20streaming%20TV.%20Publishers%20are%20also%20distributing%20full-length%20movies%20and%20TV%20on%20other%20free%20video%20platforms%20like%20The%20Roku%20Channel%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-fox-tubi-streamer-won-gen-z-grew-audience-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EFox's%20Tubi.%3C%2Fa%3E%20Some%20have%20even%20experimented%20with%20TikTok%2C%20which%20now%20allows%20videos%20up%20to%2060%20minutes%20long.%20But%20industry%20insiders%20generally%20say%20YouTube%20is%20the%20biggest%20opportunity%20because%20companies%20can%20easily%20upload%20videos%20there%2C%20control%20their%20publishing%20strategy%2C%20and%20reach%20a%20vast%20audience.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYouTube's%20appeal%20varies%20somewhat%20from%20publisher%20to%20publisher.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKids%20media%20companies%20like%20Nickelodeon%20recognize%20YouTube%20is%20increasingly%20the%20platform%20of%20choice%20for%20their%20core%20audiences.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20case%20of%20%26quot%3BLast%20Week%20Tonight%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20person%20familiar%20with%20the%20decision%20said%20the%20call%20to%20move%20up%20the%20YouTube%20drops%20was%20made%20to%20satisfy%20Oliver.%20They%20added%20that%20delaying%20the%20YouTube%20release%20hadn't%20helped%20the%20show's%20viewership%20on%20WBD's%20own%20channels%20anyway.%20This%20person%20asked%20for%20anonymity%20because%20they%20weren't%20publicly%20authorized%20to%20discuss%20the%20strategy%3B%20their%20identity%20is%20known%20to%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20companies%20like%20Fremantle%20and%20WBD%2C%20with%20huge%20catalogs%20of%20older%20shows%20and%20movies%2C%20YouTube%20can%20unearth%20pockets%20of%20viewers%20for%20even%20the%20most%20niche%20shows.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThese%20are%2010-year-old%20shows%20that%20were%20hugely%20popular%2C%26quot%3B%20Lovett%20said.%20%26quot%3BBeing%20able%20to%20air%20them%20on%20a%20%5Bfree%2C%20on-demand%20streaming%5D%20channel%20gave%20them%20a%20whole%20new%20revenue%20stream.%20This%20is%20pretty%20much%20passive%20income.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYouTube%20can%20also%20help%20a%20show%20find%20an%20audience%20it%20missed%20on%20TV.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EChannel%204%20put%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.channel4.com%2Fprogrammes%2Fhuge-homes-with-hugh-dennis%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EHuge%20Homes%20with%20Hugh%20Dennis%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%26quot%3B%20where%20the%20comedian%20takes%20viewers%20inside%20big%20houses%2C%20on%20YouTube%20after%20it%20flopped%20elsewhere.%20The%20audience%20went%20bonkers%20for%20it%20on%20YouTube%2C%20and%20then%20viewership%20on%20streaming%20ticked%20up.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20data-script%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20data-styles%3D%5C%22default-width%5C%22%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22youtube%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22embed%5C%22%3E%3Ciframe%20referrerpolicy%3D%5C%22strict-origin-when-cross-origin%5C%22%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2FFibgBAyLb10%3Ffeature%3Doembed%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Would%20You%20Live%20on%20This%20Stunning%20Island%3F%20%7C%20Huge%20Homes%20With%20Hugh%20Dennis%20%7C%20Channel%204%20Lifestyle%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22315%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2230d4b2ba-4803-419d-8948-8c95de7767ed%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EYouTube%20can%20offer%20new%20ad%20revenue%20and%20viewers%20but%20can%20be%20tricky%20to%20navigate%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ERepublishing%20full-length%20content%20successfully%20on%20YouTube%20isn't%20always%20quick%20or%20easy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShows%20are%20often%20tangled%20up%20in%20a%20knot%20of%20local%20and%20overseas%20rights%2C%20preventing%20producers%20from%20dropping%20them%20straight%20on%20YouTube.%20It%20also%20can%20take%20a%20while%20to%20figure%20out%20how%20to%20package%20up%20old%20shows%20so%20they%20land%20with%20viewers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EChannel%204%20tested%20for%20months%20to%20hone%20its%20strategy.%20The%20company%20bleeped%20swear%20words%20to%20avoid%20YouTube's%20age%20restrictions%20and%20worked%20to%20nail%20titles%2C%20thumbnails%2C%20and%20keywords%20so%20the%20platform's%20algorithm%20would%20surface%20the%20videos.%20And%20it%20had%20to%20curate%20its%20vast%20amount%20of%20material%20for%20a%20YouTube%20audience.%20It%20figured%20out%20that%20%26quot%3Bblue%20light%26quot%3B%20emergency%20services%20docs%20about%20police%20and%20ambulance%20rescues%20played%20well%20with%20viewers%2C%20for%20example.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20publishing%20to%20YouTube%2C%20media%20companies%20also%20have%20to%20reckon%20with%20the%20potential%20loss%20of%20licensing%20or%20audience%20revenue.%20That's%20why%20viewers%20tend%20to%20see%20older%20shows%20on%20YouTube%20that%20are%20of%20less%20value%20to%20other%20platforms.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20would%20be%20surprised%20if%20any%20legacy%20media%20business%20was%20not%20nervous%20about%20this%20or%20had%20any%20existential%20crisis%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Matt%20Risley%2C%20managing%20director%20of%204Studio%20at%20Channel%204.%20%26quot%3BWe%20discussed%20it%20at%20length.%26quot%3B%