20on%20AI%20leaders.%3Cp%3EWorld%20Economic%20Forum%2FGabriel%20Lado%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20CEOs%20of%20%3Ca%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22false%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgoogle-deepmind%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EGoogle%20DeepMind%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20Anthropic%20spoke%20about%20feeling%20the%20weight%20of%20responsibilities%20in%20a%20recent%20interview.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20executives%20advocated%20for%20the%20creation%20of%20regulatory%20bodies%20to%20oversee%20AI%20projects.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EBoth%20AI%20leaders%20agree%20that%20people%20should%20better%20grasp%20and%20prepare%20for%20the%20risks%20posed%20by%20advanced%20AI.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20asked%20if%20he%20ever%20worried%20about%20%26quot%3Bending%20up%20like%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flife-career-of-j-robert-oppenheimer-father-of-atomic-bomb-2023-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ERobert%20Oppenheimer%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%26quot%3B%20Google%20DeepMind's%20CEO%20Demis%20Hassabis%20said%20that%20he%20loses%20sleep%20over%20the%20idea.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20worry%20about%20those%20kinds%20of%20scenarios%20all%20the%20time.%20That's%20why%20I%20don't%20sleep%20very%20much%2C%26quot%3B%20Hassabis%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Esaid%20in%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D4poqjZlM8Lo%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Einterview%3C%2Fa%3E%20alongside%20Anthropic%20CEO%20Dario%20Amodei%20with%20The%20Economist%20editor%20in%20chief%20Zanny%20Minton%20Beddoes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20mean%2C%20there's%20a%20huge%20amount%20of%20responsibility%20on%20the%20people%20%E2%80%94%20probably%20too%20much%20%E2%80%94%20on%20the%20people%20leading%20this%20technology%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHassabis%20and%20Amodei%20agreed%20that%20advanced%20AI%20could%20present%20destructive%20potential%20whenever%20it%20becomes%20viable.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAlmost%20every%20decision%20that%20I%20make%20feels%20like%20it's%20kind%20of%20balanced%20on%20the%20edge%20of%20a%20knife%20%E2%80%94%20like%2C%20you%20know%2C%20if%20we%20don't%20build%20fast%20enough%2C%20then%20the%20authoritarian%20countries%20could%20win%2C%26quot%3B%20Amodei%20said.%20%26quot%3BIf%20we%20build%20too%20fast%2C%20then%20the%20kinds%20of%20risks%20that%20Demis%20is%20talking%20about%20and%20that%20we've%20written%20about%20a%20lot%2C%20you%20know%2C%20could%20prevail.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEither%20way%2C%20I'll%20feel%20that%20it%20was%20my%20fault%20that%2C%20you%20know%2C%20that%20we%20didn't%20make%20exactly%20the%20right%20decision%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Anthropic%20CEO%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHassabis%20said%20that%20while%20AI%20appears%20%26quot%3Boverhyped%26quot%3B%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-impact-overblown-investment-tech-stocks-billions-daron-acemoglu-mit-2024-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ein%20the%20short%20term%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20he%20worries%20that%20the%20mid-to-long-term%20consequences%20remain%20underappreciated.%20He%20promotes%20a%20balanced%20perspective%20%E2%80%94%20to%20recognize%20the%20%26quot%3Bincredible%20opportunities%26quot%3B%20afforded%20by%20AI%2C%20particularly%20in%20the%20realms%20of%20science%20and%20medicine%2C%20while%20becoming%20more%20keenly%20aware%20of%20the%20accompanying%20risks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%26quot%3B%3C%2Fstrong%3EThe%20two%20big%20risks%20that%20I%20talk%20about%20are%20bad%20actors%20repurposing%20this%20general%20purpose%20technology%20for%20harmful%20ends%20%E2%80%94%20how%20do%20we%20enable%20the%20good%20actors%20and%20restrict%20access%20to%20the%20bad%20actors%3F%26quot%3B%20Hassabis%20said.%20%26quot%3BAnd%20then%2C%20secondly%2C%20is%20the%20risk%20from%20AGI%2C%20or%20agentic%20systems%20themselves%2C%20getting%20out%20of%20control%2C%20or%20not%20having%20the%20right%20values%20or%20the%20right%20goals.%20And%20both%20of%20those%20things%20are%20critical%20to%20get%20right%2C%20and%20I%20think%20the%20whole%20world%20needs%20to%20focus%20on%20that.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBoth%20Amodei%20and%20Hassabis%20advocated%20for%20a%20governing%20body%20to%20regulate%20AI%20projects%2C%20with%20Hassabis%20pointing%20to%20the%20International%20Atomic%20Energy%20Agency%20as%20one%20potential%20model.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIdeally%20it%20would%20be%20something%20like%20the%20UN%2C%20but%20given%20the%20geopolitical%20complexities%2C%20that%20doesn't%20seem%20very%20possible%2C%26quot%3B%20Hassabis%20said.%20%26quot%3BSo%2C%20you%20know%2C%20I%20worry%20about%20all%20the%20time%2C%20and%20we%20just%20try%20to%20do%20at%20least%2C%20on%20our%20side%2C%20everything%20we%20can%20in%20the%20vicinity%20and%20influence%20that%20we%20have.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHassabis%20views%20international%20cooperation%20as%20vital.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMy%20hope%20is%2C%20you%20know%2C%20I've%20talked%20a%20lot%20in%20the%20past%20about%20a%20kind%20of%20a%20CERN%20for%20AGI%20type%20setup%2C%20where%20basically%20an%20international%20research%20collaboration%20on%20the%20last%20sort%20of%20few%20steps%20that%20we%20need%20to%20take%20towards%20building%20the%20first%20AGIs%2C%26quot%3B%20Hassabis%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBoth%20leaders%20urged%20a%20better%20understanding%20of%20the%20sheer%20force%20for%20change%20they%20expect%20AI%20to%20be%20%E2%80%94%20and%20for%20societies%20to%20begin%20planning%20accordingly.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe're%20on%20the%20eve%20of%20something%20that%20has%20great%20challenges%2C%20right%3F%20It's%20going%20to%20greatly%20upend%20the%20balance%20of%20power%2C%26quot%3B%20Amodei%20said.%20%26quot%3BIf%20someone%20dropped%20a%20new%20country%20into%20the%20world%20%E2%80%94%2010%20million%20people%20smarter%20than%20any%20human%20alive%20today%20%E2%80%94%20you%20know%2C%20you'd%20ask%20the%20question%2C%20'What%20is%20t