6a67a69-9856-44a3-96d8-bc2b994b7834%5C%22%3EI%20was%20charmed%20by%20UK%20life%20but%20it%20wasn't%20perfect%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20prepared%20a%20thesis%20proposal%20to%20study%20social%20media%20influencers%20and%20sent%20it%20to%20the%20University%20of%20Manchester.%20Four%20months%20later%2C%20I%20was%20standing%20inside%20Manchester%20Airport%20with%20two%20pet%20carriers%2C%20two%20suitcases%2C%20and%20one%20new%20life%20ahead%20of%20me.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20was%20immediately%20charmed.%20The%20university%20had%20tiny%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fafternoon-tea-belvoir-castle-photos-2022-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etea%20rooms%3C%2Fa%3E%20with%20kettles%2C%20a%20sink%2C%20and%20space%20to%20store%20cups%2C%20saucers%2C%20and%20sugar%20cubes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20marveled%20at%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flawyer-quit-left-london-moved-small-town-2024-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eslower%20pace%20of%20life%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20work-life%20balance.%20%26quot%3BRead%2C%20read%2C%20read.%20Walk.%20Exercise.%20Contemplate.%20Then%2C%20you%20will%20write%2C%26quot%3B%20one%20of%20my%20two%20German%20supervisors%20told%20me.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20that%20end%2C%20the%20university%20encouraged%20travel.%20Many%20of%20us%20took%20extended%20weekends%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fscotland-vs-us-family-travel-2024-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etrek%20through%20Scotland%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Wales%2C%20down%20to%20London%2C%20and%20elsewhere%20abroad.%20Transportation%20was%20cheap%2C%20and%20vacation%20time%20was%20plenty.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDespite%20Friday%20stops%20at%20the%20local%20chippy%20and%20regularly%20%26quot%3Bgoing%20for%20a%20curry%2C%26quot%3B%20I%20lost%20more%20than%2020%20pounds%20and%20reversed%20my%20insulin%20resistance%20thanks%20to%20the%20UK's%20pedestrian-friendly%20lifestyle.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20US%2C%20I%20was%20a%20c