ps%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fnew-bat-coronavirus-capable-of-infecting-humans-discovered-in-china-7766571%5C%22%3EHKU5-CoV-2%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20similar%20to%20the%20virus%20that%20caused%20the%20COVID-19%20pandemic%2C%20has%20been%20identified%20in%20China.%20The%20discovery%20was%20made%20by%20a%20team%20of%20virologists%20led%20by%20Shi%20Zhengli%2C%20often%20referred%20to%20as%20%26quot%3BBatwoman%26quot%3B%20for%20her%20extensive%20research%20on%20coronaviruses%20at%20the%20Wuhan%20Institute.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20is%20HKU5-CoV-2%20or%20Bat%20Virus%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHKU5-CoV-2%20is%20a%20newly%20discovered%20bat%20coronavirus%20that%20belongs%20to%20the%20merbecovirus%20subgenus%2C%20which%20also%20includes%20the%20virus%20responsible%20for%20Middle%20East%20respiratory%20syndrome%20(MERS).%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EScientists%20found%20that%20it%20can%20bind%20to%20human%20ACE2%20receptors%2C%20similar%20to%20SARS-CoV-2%20(the%20virus%20behind%20COVID-19).%20This%20suggests%20it%20has%20the%20potential%20for%20animal-to-human%20transmission.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EExperts%20note%20that%20HKU5-CoV-2%20has%20a%20lower%20binding%20affinity%20to%20human%20ACE2%20than%20SARS-CoV-2%2C%20and%20its%20ability%20to%20infect%20humans%20on%20a%20large%20scale%20remains%20uncertain.%20More%20research%20is%20needed%20to%20determine%20if%20it%20poses%20a%20serious%20health%20threat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20It%20Can%20Affect%20Humans%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EBinds%20to%20human%20ACE2%20receptors%3A%20The%20virus%20can%20attach%20to%20ACE2%2C%20the%20same%20receptor%20used%20by%20SARS-CoV-2%20(Covid-19)%20to%20infect%20human%20cells.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EPotential%20for%20spillover%3A%20Researchers%20found%20that%20when%20HKU5-CoV-2%20was%20taken%20from%20bats%2C%20it%20could%20infect%20human%20cells%20and%20lab-grown%20tiny%20lung%20or%20gut%20tissues.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EIntermediate%20hosts%3A%20The%20virus%20binds%20not%20just%20to%20human%20ACE2%20but%20also%20to%20multiple%20mammalian%20species%2C%20meaning%20it%20could%20spread%20through%20an%20intermediate%20animal%20before%20reaching%20humans.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ELower%20efficiency%20than%20Covid-19%3A%20While%20it%20can%20infect%20human%20cells%2C%20scientists%20have%20said%20its%20ability%20to%20do%20so%20is%20significantly%20weaker%20than%20SARS-CoV-2.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20research%20team%2C%20led%20by%20Shi%20Zhengli%2C%20a%20leading%20virologist%20from%20Wuhan%20Institute%20of%20Virology%2C%20pointed%20out%20that%20while%20HKU5-CoV-2%20shows%20a%20higher%20adaptation%20to%20human%20ACE2%20than%20its%20earlier%20versions%2C%20it%20does%20not%20pose%20an%20immediate%20pandemic%20threat.%20Continuous%20monitoring%20is%20still%20needed%20to%20track%20any%20potential%20mutations%20that%20could%20increase%20its%20infectiousness.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHKU5-CoV-2%20or%20Bat%20Virus%3A%20Symptoms%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20no%20confirmed%20cases%20of%20HKU5-CoV-2%20in%20humans%20yet%2C%20so%20its%20symptoms%20are%20unknown.%20But%20since%20it%20belongs%20to%20the%20same%20subgenus%20as%20MERS%20and%20COVID-19%2C%20it%20might%20cause%20similar%20respiratory%20symptoms%2C%20such%20as%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EFever%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ECough%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EShortness%20of%20breath%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ESore%20throat%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EFatigue%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EBody%20aches%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20the%20HKU5-CoV-2%20or%20Bat%20Virus%20can%20spread%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20can%20spread%20to%20humans%20in%20two%20possible%20ways%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EDirect%20transmission%20from%20bats%3A%20If%20people%20come%20into%20contact%20with%20infected%20bats%20or%20their%20bodily%20fluids%20(like%20saliva%2C%20urine%2C%20or%20feces)%2C%20they%20could%20get%20infected.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThrough%20an%20intermediate%20host%3A%20The%20virus%20might%20first%20infect%20another%20animal%20(like%20a%20mammal)%20before%20jumping%20to%20humans%2C%20similar%20to%20how%20some%20past%20coronaviruses%20spread.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1740224160000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2022-01%2Fm3jsn8hg_bat-generic-bats-generic-pixabay_625x300_28_January_22.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fwhat-you-need-to-know-about-the-new-bat-virus-hku5-cov-2-symptoms-how-it-can-affect-humans-7767902%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20newly%20discovered%20bat%20coronavirus%2C%20HKU5-CoV-2%2C%20similar%20to%20the%20virus%20that%20caused%20the%20COVID-19%20pandemic%2C%20has%20been%20identified%20in%20China.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fwhat-you-need-to-know-about-the-new-bat-virus-hku5-cov-2-symptoms-how-it-can-affect-humans-7767902%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Delhi%20showdown%3A%20CM%20Rekha%20Gupta-led%20govt%20to%20table%20CAG%20reports%20next%20week%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1740223895000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-118479183%2Cimgsize-1356211.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Findia%2Fdelhi-govt-to-table-cag-reports-on-february-25%2Farticleshow%2F118479158.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Delhi%20government%20will%20table%20the%20long-pending%20CAG%20reports%20examining%20the%20previous%20AAP%20administration's%20performance%20in%20the%20Assembly%20on%20February%2025.%20BJP%20MLA%20Vijender%20Gupta%2C%20the%20newly%20elected%20Speaker%2C%20confirmed%20the%20reports'%20tabling.%20The%20BJP%20alleges%20AAP%20delayed%20the%20reports%20to%20conceal%20corruption%2C%20while%20CM%20Rekha%20Gupta%20defends%20her%20swift%20actions.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20NEWS%20DESK