20in%20the%20region%2C%20Khang%20doesn't%20believe%20the%20US%20has%20undue%20leverage%20over%20Europe.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNo%20matter%20how%20many%20different%20ways%20you%20cut%20it%2C%20the%20damage%20to%20the%20European%20economy%20through%20the%20trade%20channel%20specifically%20will%20be%20not%20as%20adverse%20as%20it%20would%20be%20for%20some%20of%20the%20other%20countries%2C%26quot%3B%20Khang%20said.%20%26quot%3BThat%20makes%20it%20a%20little%20less%20of%20a%20downside%20scenario%2C%20from%20the%20tariff%20standpoint.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EConcerns%20about%20tariffs%20and%20the%20economy%20pushed%20Europe's%20already-cheap%20stock%20valuations%20to%20irresistible%20levels%2C%20Ruggirello%20remarked.%20The%20investment%20chief%20noted%20that%20the%20S%26amp%3BP%20500's%20forward%20earnings%20multiple%20is%20well%20above%20that%20of%20the%20Stoxx%20600%2C%20and%20it's%20also%20far%20higher%20than%20when%20Trump%20took%20office%20eight%20years%20ago.%20He%20believes%20investors%20are%20now%20adjusting%20their%20portfolios%20accordingly.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20train%20left%20the%20station%2C%20but%20the%20ride%20can%20go%20on%20for%20quite%20some%20time%20%E2%80%94%20if%20not%20the%20whole%20year%2C%26quot%3B%20Ruggirello%20said%20of%20European%20stocks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%220150b424-67dd-486f-b575-5dde14e8c5a6%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EBeaten-down%20foreign%20stocks%20may%20get%20a%20boost%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20cheap%20valuations%20only%20explain%20part%20of%20this%20major%20turnaround%20in%20international%20markets.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEquity%20investing%20is%20ultimately%20about%20determining%20how%20much%20profit%20a%20company%20can%20produce%2C%20when%20it%20can%20do%20so%2C%20and%20at%20what%20pace.%20Considering%20how%20much%20better%20earnings%20have%20been%20for%20US-based%20companies%2C%20Franklin%20Templeton%20strategist%20Chris%20Galipeau%20said%20their%20dominant%20run%20is%20no%20fluke.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cf