r%20be%20ignored.%20A%20sense%20of%20urgency%20was%20shared%20by%20the%20fund%20anchors%2C%20who%20together%20took%20the%20bold%20step%20to%20address%20the%20glaring%20gap%20in%20funding%20for%20grassroots%20queer%20initiatives%20in%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20motivation%20behind%20the%20fund%3F%20A%20growing%20awareness%20of%20the%20sluggish%20pace%20of%20legislative%20and%20social%20change%20in%20India%2C%20compounded%20by%20the%20lack%20of%20corporate%20funding%20reaching%20the%20very%20organisations%20that%20are%20fighting%20for%20the%20rights%20of%20the%20LGBTQIA%2B%20community%20at%20the%20grassroots%20level.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECommenting%20on%20the%20launch%2C%20Parmesh%20Shahani%2C%20Head%20of%20the%20Godrej%20DEI%20Lab%2C%20highlighted%20the%20%3Cem%3EPride%20Fund%E2%80%99s%3C%2Fem%3E%20pioneering%20role%20in%20India%3A%20%E2%80%9CThe%20%3Cem%3EPride%20Fund%3C%2Fem%3E%20marks%20a%20historic%20milestone%20%E2%80%94%20it%20is%20a%20first-of-its-kind%20initiative%20in%20India%2C%20created%20by%20queer%20community%20members%20for%20the%20community.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20fund%20reflects%20our%20shared%20vision%20of%20equity%20and%20inclusion%20by%20directly%20tackling%20the%20systemic%20barriers%20that%20have%20long%20marginalised%20LGBTQIA%2B%20individuals.%20With%20only%2027%25%20of%20NGOs%20serving%20the%20community%20having%20a%20national%20presence%2C%20we%20aim%20to%20empower%20these%20communities%20by%20providing%20targeted%20support%20and%20resources.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COur%20goal%20is%20to%20ensure%20access%20to%20safety%2C%20health%2C%20justice%2C%20and%20opportunities%20that%20have%20been%20denied%20to%20them%20for%20far%20too%20long.%E2%80%9D%20He%20added%2C%20%E2%80%9CBy%20addressing%20these%20pressing%20needs%2C%20we%20hope%20to%20create%20a%20ripple%20effect%20that%20leads%20to%20a%20more%20inclusive%20and%20equitable%20society%20%E2%80%94%20one%20that%20truly%20embodies%20the%20spirit%20of%20a%20Viksit%20Bhar