n%20the%20jungle%20is%20poor%2C%20the%20data%20is%20stored%20offline%20and%20syncs%20once%20network%20access%20is%20available.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%227521127830%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFoot%20patrol%20officers%20are%20crucial%20in%20this%20process.%20These%20officers%2C%20often%20working%20in%20risky%20conditions%2C%20navigate%20dense%20forests%20and%20confront%20potential%20elephant%20encounters%20to%20gather%20real-time%20data.%20%E2%80%9CThere%20have%20been%20times%20when%20we%20have%20escaped%20a%20massive%20attack%2C%E2%80%9D%20shares%20Om%20Prakash.%20Their%20efforts%20ensure%20accurate%20tracking%2C%20forming%20the%20backbone%20of%20the%20AI%20system.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%20620px)%20100vw%2C%20620px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F02%2FAdobe-Express-file-71_11zon-1739872094.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22620%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Foot%20officers%20documenting%20elephant%20movements%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F02%2FAdobe-Express-file-71_11zon-1739872094.jpg%20620w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F02%2FAdobe-Express-file-71_11zon-1739872094-300x169.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F02%2FAdobe-Express-file-71_11zon-1739872094-500x281.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F02%2FAdobe-Express-file-71_11zon-1739872094-150x84.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-406833%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22349%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20foot%20officers%20add%20the%20information%20to%20the%20service%20via%20the%20app.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20recorded%20data%20is%20processed%20using%20Quantum%20GIS%20(QGIS)%2C%20an%20open-source%20mapping%20software%20which%20plots%20elephant%20movements%20and%20sets%20a%2010-km%20buffer%20zone%20around%20the%20location.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAI%20automatically%20sends%20alerts%20via%20SMSs%2C%20calls%2C%20and%20WhatsApp%20messages%2C%20to%20registered%20villagers%2C%20local%20leaders%2C%20and%20forest%20department%20officials%20in%20at-risk%20areas.%20%E2%80%9CThey%20don%E2%80%99t%20have%20to%20install%20any%20app%3B%20they%20just%20need%20to%20register%20their%20mobile%20numbers%2C%E2%80%9D%20Varun%20explains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%229669016977%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20automation%2C%3Cem%3E%20M%3C%2Fem%3Eunaadi%20is%20still%20carried%20out%20manually%20as%20a%20second%20line%20of%20defence%2C%20ensuring%20those%20without%20phones%20or%20network%20access%20are%20also%20informed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%20620px)%20100vw%2C%20620px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F02%2FAdobe-Express-file-72_11zon-1739872171.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22620%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Foot%20officers%20taking%20a%20picture%20of%20elephant%20marks%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F02%2FAdobe-Express-file-72_11zon-1739872171.jpg%20620w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F02%2FAdobe-Express-file-72_11zon-1739872171-300x169.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F02%2FAdobe-Express-file-72_11zon-1739872171-500x281.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2